  "title": "中山區少女心咖啡廳 &#8211; Hera Cafe",
  "excerpt": "<p>本來只是想找一間普通的、可以開晚一點的咖啡廳，結果卻意外選了一間非常粉藍粉紅色系的少女咖啡廳⋯⋯ 進店的時候門&#8230;</p>\n",
  "feature_image_url": "https://backend.wildsky.cc/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/IMG_9196-e1563086094258.png",
  "content": "\n<p>本來只是想找一間普通的、可以開晚一點的咖啡廳，結果卻意外選了一間非常粉藍粉紅色系的少女咖啡廳⋯⋯</p>\n\n\n\n<p>進店的時候門口沒人，便逕自往地下室走去，到 B1 時傻眼，因為眼前整個配置就是夢幻少女的感覺，旁邊甚至還有女僕裝的人（後來才知道原來是顧客XD）選了個沙發位置坐下後就開始點餐。</p>\n\n\n\n<!--more-->\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img width=\"700\" height=\"525\" src=\"https://blog.wildsky.cc/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/8146.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-1565\" srcset=\"https://backend.wildsky.cc/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/8146.png 700w, https://backend.wildsky.cc/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/8146-300x225.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>店內的位置大約 20 人左右，除了一個沙發外其他都是正常的普通座位。缺點是這邊沒有什麼插座，所以可能比較不適合來這邊使用筆電。三點的時候位置大約七分滿，平常來應該都會有位置。</p>\n\n\n\n<p>翻來翻去發現沒有正餐（我好餓啊 QQ），只好點了摩卡和蜂蜜布丁戚風。</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img width=\"700\" height=\"735\" src=\"https://blog.wildsky.cc/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/IMG_1168-e1563086823706-1.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-1561\" srcset=\"https://backend.wildsky.cc/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/IMG_1168-e1563086823706-1.png 700w, https://backend.wildsky.cc/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/IMG_1168-e1563086823706-1-286x300.png 286w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\" /><figcaption>在一間少女心的店裡，桌上有個用來拍照的花也不為過吧XD</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>價格方面還算是親民，戚風 150，摩卡 160。不收服務費，點餐後先結帳。</p>\n\n\n\n<p>這邊也附上菜單：</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-jetpack-slideshow aligncenter\" data-effect=\"slide\"><div class=\"wp-block-jetpack-slideshow_container swiper-container\"><ul class=\"wp-block-jetpack-slideshow_swiper-wrapper swiper-wrapper\"><li class=\"wp-block-jetpack-slideshow_slide swiper-slide\"><figure><img width=\"768\" height=\"1024\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-block-jetpack-slideshow_image wp-image-1562\" data-id=\"1562\" src=\"https://blog.wildsky.cc/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/1.png\" srcset=\"https://backend.wildsky.cc/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/1.png 768w, https://backend.wildsky.cc/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/1-225x300.png 225w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px\" /></figure></li><li class=\"wp-block-jetpack-slideshow_slide swiper-slide\"><figure><img width=\"768\" height=\"1024\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-block-jetpack-slideshow_image wp-image-1563\" data-id=\"1563\" src=\"https://blog.wildsky.cc/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/3.png\" srcset=\"https://backend.wildsky.cc/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/3.png 768w, https://backend.wildsky.cc/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/3-225x300.png 225w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px\" /></figure></li><li class=\"wp-block-jetpack-slideshow_slide swiper-slide\"><figure><img width=\"768\" height=\"1024\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-block-jetpack-slideshow_image wp-image-1564\" data-id=\"1564\" src=\"https://blog.wildsky.cc/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/2.png\" srcset=\"https://backend.wildsky.cc/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/2.png 768w, https://backend.wildsky.cc/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/2-225x300.png 225w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px\" /></figure></li></ul><a class=\"wp-block-jetpack-slideshow_button-prev swiper-button-prev swiper-button-white\" role=\"button\"></a><a class=\"wp-block-jetpack-slideshow_button-next swiper-button-next swiper-button-white\" role=\"button\"></a><a aria-label=\"Pause Slideshow\" class=\"wp-block-jetpack-slideshow_button-pause\" role=\"button\"></a><div class=\"wp-block-jetpack-slideshow_pagination swiper-pagination swiper-pagination-white\"></div></div></div>\n\n\n\n<p>吃完甜點後就開始看自己帶來的書，中間又來了另一個女僕和一組日本人客人。店員的日語講得很流利。感覺來這邊的人都是為了拍網美照，看書看到一半所有人的在四處拍照，樣況也是有些壯觀。XD</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>基本資訊</h2>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>地址：台北市大同區承德路二段1巷7號（地圖放下方）</li><li>交通：中山站五號出口走路兩分鐘</li><li>營業時間：<ul><li>週四 公休</li><li>週三 – 週一 12:00 – 19:00</li></ul></li><li>Facebook 粉專：<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/heracafe.co/\">https://www.facebook.com/heracafe.co/</a></li></ul>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"wifi-%e5%af%86%e7%a2%bc\">Wifi 密碼</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>雖然市內仍可收到 4G 訊號，但還是附一下：</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img width=\"700\" height=\"525\" src=\"https://blog.wildsky.cc/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/IMG_0190-e1563087471365-1.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-1567\" srcset=\"https://backend.wildsky.cc/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/IMG_0190-e1563087471365-1.png 700w, https://backend.wildsky.cc/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/IMG_0190-e1563087471365-1-300x225.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<h3>地圖</h3>\n\n\n<div class=\"googlemaps\">\n\t\t\t\t<iframe width=\"700\" height=\"500\" frameborder=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\" marginheight=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\"  src=\"https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m14!1m8!1m3!1d1807.217141193354!2d121.51877610926209!3d25.0532656944446!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x0:0x90400334233464c2!2zSGVyYSBDYWZlIC0g5oia6aKo6JuL57OVIHwg5omL5bel55Sc6bueIHwg5LiN6ZmQ5pmC5ZKW5ZWh5buz!5e0!3m2!1szh-TW!2stw!4v1563087516419!5m2!1szh-TW!2stw\"></iframe>\n\t\t\t</div>\n"
